      "value": "<p>You make a strong forward Strike with an unarmed or brawling weapon at a creature within melee reach that ignores the target's hardness, if it has any.</p><p>If you spend a focus point when using this action, you can follow up with a second Strike at the same multi-attack penalty and hardness ignoring property as the first Strike. If your second Strike hits, you can attempt to Shove your target at the same multi-attack penalty as the second Strike.</p><p>This would count as three attacks for the purposes of incurring multi attack penalty.</p>"
